Package com.camerontec.catalys.mis.ler

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ILogEventsRepositoryReader
    This interface defines the operations providing read access to the MA's Log Events Repository.
    ISearchContext
    Reusable search context returned as part of SearchResults by ILogEventsRepositoryReader.search(java.util.Map, Long, Long, DateFilter, java.util.EnumSet, String, java.util.List, int, int, int)
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    HighlightedLogEvent
    A LogEvent with a list of highlighted text fragments corresponding to search hits in its message.
    SearchResults<T>
    Instances of this class represent the results of a search in the log events repository and are composed of: The total number of results returned by the search.
    TailResults
    Instances of this class represent the results of a tailing search in the log events repository and are composed of: The total number of results returned by the search.
    TextFragment
    A tuple (offset, length) representing a fragment of text.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    LogEventsRepositoryAccessException
    Instances of this exception are thrown to indicate that an error has occurred while attempting to access the log events repository.
